# Git Workflow

## Branch Naming

**Format**: `<type>/<area>-<short-desc>-<task-number>`

- **Types**: `feature`, `fix`, `chore`, `docs`, `refactor`
- **Areas**: `api`, `fe`, `retro`, `poker`, `slack`, `notifications`, `teams`, `storage`
- **Example**: `feature/api-notifications-mark-read-22`

## Commit Messages

**Format**: `<type>(<scope>): <description>`

- **Example**: `feat(api): add notifications controller (Task #22)`

## Before Opening PR

1. Update task tracker (`tasks/tasks-csharp-pass-through-api.md`) to "In progress"
2. Run linters and tests (must pass 100%)
3. Update coverage tracker (`documentation/plans/csharp-api-coverage-tracker.md`)
4. Verify feature flag works in BOTH states

## Commit Rules

- NEVER force-push to shared branches
- NEVER skip tests before committing
- NEVER commit without running linters
